  "texts": [
    "Chen et al. [5] trained RNN-based BBO algorithms using privileged access to gradient computations of the fitness function at training time.",
    "Furthermore, Chen et al. [6], Dery et al.",
    "[7] used large pre-collected datasets to directly train a T5 Encoder-Decoder architecture [35] for BBO, called OptFormer.",
    "Krishnamoorthy et al. [15] later on investigated the usage of generating offline data for training autoregressive BBO models.",
    "All of these approaches trained large sequence models leveraging large programmatically generated or augmented task spaces to induce in-context learning across long timescales."
  ],
